title: Orphans of the Tower  (2007) (Sosich)cbr
description:
Placed in an orphanage since his young age,theo is convinced that an invisible tower raises up from the heart of New York and that strange ghosts are coming to take him.
With the help of artificial intelligence who is convinced of being a human being,and mysterious monk from the underground who honors an old debt,Theo will take part in a battle without mercy where the control of the city is only one of the challenges...

enjoy
